::Aerotaur::
       He gradually makes his way back to his cavern home.  With a sense of 
completion he leaves the cave and takes flight again for the Maximal base.  
Upon his arrival he lands and walks inside announcing his arrival.  "Hello 
Maximals Aerotaur's back."
